    {
      "id": "640ef969e60035000099c0db",
      "text": "cf. [臓器くじ]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1678702954,
      "updated": 1678702956
    },
    {
      "id": "640ef96be60035000099c0dd",
      "text": " [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/臓器くじ 臓器くじ - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1678702956,
      "updated": 1678702956
    },
    {
      "id": "640ef96be60035000099c0de",
      "text": " >「臓器くじ」は以下のような社会制度を指す。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1678702956,
      "updated": 1678702956
    },
    {
      "id": "640ef96be60035000099c0df",
      "text": " > 1. 公平なくじで健康な人をランダムに一人選び、殺す。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1678702956,
      "updated": 1678702956
    },
    {
      "id": "640ef96be60035000099c0e0",
      "text": " > 2. その人の臓器を全て取り出し、[臓器移植]が必要な人々に配る。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1678702956,
      "updated": 1678702956
    },
